longBusinessSummary: Ainsworth Game Technology Limited designs, develops, manufactures, sells, distributes, and services electronic gaming machines, and other related equipment and services. The company also provides online real money and social games. It has operations in Australia, North America, Latin America, Europe, New Zealand, South Africa, Asia, and internationally. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Newington, Australia. Ainsworth Game Technology Limited is a subsidiary of Novomatic AG.
